data.name: Label6.Text
data.value: The 5-star Westin Cairo Golf Resort & Spa is located in the upscale Katameya Dunes, offering rooms and suites with views of gardens, pools, or the golf course. Amenities include a heated outdoor pool, Heavenly® spa, fitness center, and Mediterranean dining. The Pyramids are 26 miles away, and Cairo International Airport is 18 miles from the property.
